OL,3,CWater bills to rise by an average of
OL,4,C#31 a year over next five years
OL,6,FThis comes as around 60,000 people in
OL,7,FSouth Hampshire are without water for
OL,8,Fa second day running following a fault
OL,9,Fat a Southern Water supply works.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, Thames Water has been
OL,12,Fhanded an #18.2 million penalty for
OL,13,Fbreaking dividend payment rules, Ofwat
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed said
OL,17,F"the public are right to be angry" and
OL,18,Fblamed the previous Tory government
OL,19,Ffor the state of the water industry.
