OL,3,CWater bills to rise by an average of
OL,4,C#31 a year over next five years
OL,6,FHe said: "Under the Conservatives, our
OL,7,Fsewage system crumbled. They
OL,8,Firresponsibly let water companies
OL,9,Fdivert customers' money to line the
OL,10,Fpockets of their bosses and
OL,11,Fshareholders.
OL,13,F"The public are right to be angry
OL,14,Fafter they have been left to pay the
OL,15,Fprice of Conservative failure.
OL,17,F"This Labour Government will ringfence
OL,18,Fmoney earmarked for investment so it
OL,19,Fcan never be diverted for bonuses and
OL,20,Fshareholder payouts. We will clean up
OL,21,Four rivers, lakes and seas for good."
