OL,3,CWater bills to rise by an average of
OL,4,C#31 a year over next five years
OL,6,FOfwat chief executive David Black
OL,7,Fsaid: "Today marks a significant
OL,8,Fmoment. It provides water companies
OL,9,Fwith an opportunity to regain
OL,10,Fcustomers' trust by using this #104
OL,11,Fbillion upgrade to turn around their
OL,12,Fenvironmental record and improve
OL,13,Fservices to customers.
OL,15,F"Water companies now need to rise to
OL,16,Fthis challenge, customers will rightly
OL,17,Fexpect them to show they can deliver
OL,18,Fsignificant improvement over time to
OL,19,Fjustify the increase in bills.
