OL,6,F"We recognise it is a difficult time
OL,7,Ffor many, and we are acutely aware of
OL,8,Fthe impact that bill increases will
OL,9,Fhave for some customers. That is why
OL,10,Fit is vital that companies are
OL,11,Fstepping up their support for
OL,12,Fcustomers who struggle to pay."
